metadata.name: The Secret
metadata.description:
The Secret

The Secret is the first piece of the women's series to be made into NFT.

A woman is a human species with a lot of details, secrets and delightful beauty. Since the history of humanity, it has experienced quite different periods. If you had asked me, "What does femininity experience during this period, what exactly does femininity look like?" on the day we arrived as a result of all these variable periods, I would have said "that's how it is". Beautiful, embellished but bored. There are many details, not just these feelings.

Woman,
  The woman who bailed us out into feelings we'd never reach the end of.

Nikos Kazantzakis' Zorba said that the woman is a secret. Yes like that.
